{"type":null,"faqId":45414,"title":"华为盒子是否支持蓝牙？如何连接蓝牙设备？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-bottom:0.2777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>支持。可通过蓝牙连接蓝牙音响、官方选配的蓝牙遥控器及蓝牙无线手柄。连接方式如下：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">连接指定的蓝牙遥控器</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>靠近华为盒子（1米内）。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 2  </span><span>请同时按住遥控器“</span><span class=\"s1\">OK</span><span>”和“</span><span class=\"s1\">音量+</span><span> ”约8秒后松开。即可完成配对。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 3  </span><span>等待一会，若遥控器能够使用，则配对成功。配对成功后，下次可直接使用，无需再配对。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165034\" style=\"width:4.342361in;height:2.44375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=165035\" style=\"width:4.342361in;height:2.44375in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">连接其他蓝牙设备：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 1  </span><span>进入“</span><span class=\"s1\">设置 &gt; 网络 &gt; 蓝牙</span><span>”，此时盒子将进入蓝牙配对状态。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 2  </span><span>启动蓝牙设备的蓝牙功能。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 3  </span><span>在盒子搜出的蓝牙设备上点击OK，启动配对。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">步骤 4  </span><span>当蓝牙设备名称出现在电视画面，并显示已连接。表示配对成功。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">----结束</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":242,"faqType":"安装产品","useful":5,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"934","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Setting-Up","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442557780000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M330","visitedTimes":65,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"连接,蓝牙","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}